text: Jango Fett is a Star Wars bounty hunter and the genetic template of the Clone troopers for the Clone Wars. He made his first appearance in Attack of the Clones (2002). ==Portrayals== As with his clones and Boba Fett, he is portrayed by Temuera Morrison.
